 158px; max-width: 170px; overflow: hidden; flex: 1 1 auto; min-width: 158px;"><img decoding="async" alt="" role="presentation" aria-hidden="true" src="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2022/10/21/metro-exodus-1666390989462.png?crop=16%3A9&amp;width=158" class="jsx-2920405963 progressive-image jsx-3998823930 image aspect-ratio aspect-ratio-16-9 jsx-1330092051 jsx-3166191823 rounded" srcset="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2022/10/21/metro-exodus-1666390989462.png?crop=16%3A9&amp;width=158 1x, https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2022/10/21/metro-exodus-1666390989462.png?crop=16%3A9&amp;width=158&amp;dpr=2 2x" style="position: relative; width: 170px; aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 6px; background-color: var(--theme-elements-background-surfaceColor); display: block;"></button><button type="button" aria-label="Open Slideshow" class="jsx-3733722558 gallery-image" style="font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.15; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; outline-width: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; width: 158px; max-width: 170px; overflow: hidden; flex: 1 1 auto; min-width: 158px;"><img decoding="async" alt="" role="presentation" aria-hidden="true" src="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2022/10/21/total-war-three-kingdoms-1666390989469.png?crop=16%3A9&amp;width=158" class="jsx-2920405963 progressive-image jsx-3998823930 image aspect-ratio aspect-ratio-16-9 jsx-1330092051 jsx-3166191823 rounded" srcset="https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2022/10/21/total-war-three-kingdoms-1666390989469.png?crop=16%3A9&amp;width=158 1x, https://assets-prd.ignimgs.com/2022/10/21/total-war-three-kingdoms-1666390989469.png?crop=16%3A9&amp;width=158&amp;dpr=2 2x" style="position: relative; width: 170px; aspect-ratio: 16 / 9; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 6px; background-color: var(--theme-elements-background-surfaceColor); display: block;"></button></div></div></div></output><p style="margin: var(--veryCompactSpacer) 0; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;">Turning to real game benchmarks, we get our best view of how our three RTX 4090s shape up against one another, as well as a selection of last generation cards. A quick glance at the bars shows that they’re extremely close. Look at the specific results, but against the MSI Suprim Liquid X, the Gigabyte Gaming OC averaged 4% faster at 1080p, 5% faster at 1440p, and 2% faster at 4K. Against the Founders Edition, it averaged 1% faster across the board.</p><p style="margin: var(--veryCompactSpacer) 0; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;">Let’s be real here: this is a 4K gaming card, so let’s hone in on those figures. Note that due to our testing routine last generation and the availability of the RTX 3090 Ti, those results are missing from several of the expanded tests.</p><p style="margin: var(--veryCompactSpacer) 0; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;">At 4K, the nearness of these cards is plain as day. Against the Suprim Liquid X, the Gaming OC is 3% faster. Against the Founders Edition, it pulls 2% ahead. That sounds slight and it is: in most cases, the cards are within 2-3 frames of each other with the biggest difference being an 8 FPS lead in Wolfenstein: Youngblood… at a high enough frame rate that it’s almost unnoticeable.</p><p style="margin: var(--veryCompactSpacer) 0; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;">These results are much the same as we found last generation. We’ll have to see how the rest of the 40-series turns out, but the fact is that these cards all perform extremely close to one another, and that’s by design. Consider it a kind of performance guarantee when you’re opting into a certain tier of card.</p><aside class="bordered-box jsx-4023299490 scaled" style="padding: var(--roomySpacer); border: 0.25em solid var(--theme-elements-text-default); color: var(--theme-elements-text-default); border-radius: 24px; transform: scale(0.85);"><h2 style="font-weight: 900;">Purchasing Guide</h2><p style="overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;">The Gigabyte GeForce RTX 4090 Gaming OC 24G is available from most major technology retailers, including Amazon, Best Buy, and Newegg, at an MSRP of $1699.</p></aside><p style="margin: var(--veryCompactSpacer) 0; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;"></p></section></section><div class="jsx-3103488995 verdict article-section" style="color: var(--theme-elements-text-default); font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 32px; overflow: hidden;"><h3 class="jsx-3103488995 verdict-header" style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 1.5rem;">Verdict</h3><div class="jsx-3103488995 article-section" style="color: var(--theme-elements-text-default); font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 32px; overflow: hidden;">So is the Gigabyte GeForce RTX 4090 Gaming OC 24G worth buying? At $100 over the cost of the Founders Edition with a 2% performance gain, it may not seem like it at first. But as an enthusiast card, part of what you’re paying for is the potential to push it further than the base specs it ships with. With such a large cooler and ample thermal headroom, the potential for overclocking is greater with the Gaming OC than the FE, even if you keep things simple and click the “Auto OC” button in MSI Afterburner or your monitoring tool of choice. At $1700, this entire class of card is aimed at exactly that type of gamer. The other element is style. Looks may not be as important as performance, but they matter, especially if you’re building a showpiece rig to run the latest games. The Gaming OC isn’t the flashiest card but it earns definite style points over the comparatively boring FE, even if you can’t see the RGB on its fans. And perhaps just as important, a $100 price premium may not seem like as much once the Founders Edition becomes difficult to find (which is already the case). The Gaming OC isn’t the cheapest card, but it’s far from the most expensive. When you add in the slight out of box edge, better overclocking potential, cool temps, and quiet fans, you’re left with a card that’s a solid and satisfying choice for a cutting edge gaming PC.</div></div><div class="qxyz-EY_r1E2m202l4E2m3Ey qxyz-CHDoFXXn1IPlCIzjDI6" id=""><div class="jsx-1301291350 bobble bobble-1 pogocnt pg-article" style="width: 876px; display: flex; position: relative; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; margin: 0px auto; height: auto; overflow: hidden;"><div data-mix-name="secondaryMedrec" data-pos="1" data-pogo-hide="1" class="jsx-4140182438 pogo-slot" style="display: flex; position: relative; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; margin: 0px auto; height: auto; overflow: hidden; flex: 1 1 0%;"></div></div></div></div><div class="jsx-2880685507 right-rail" style="grid-column: 2 / auto;"><br></div></div></div>', 'published', 1);

